Stores user account information.

Goods

Stores all product details in the warehouse.

Stock History

Stores all stock changes and updates.

6. Installation Guide
Step 1: Install XAMPP

Download and install XAMPP.

Step 2: Copy Project

Place the system folder inside:

xampp/htdocs/

Example:

xampp/htdocs/goods-management
Step 3: Start Services

Open XAMPP Control Panel and start:

Apache

MySQL

Step 4: Create Database

Open your browser and go to:

http://localhost/phpmyadmin

Create a database called:

warehouse

Import or create the required tables.

Step 5: Run the System

Open the system in a browser:

http://localhost/budget_supermarket

You will see the login page.

